it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface

Class OWLEnquirer.ClassRestriction

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLEnquirer.ClassRestriction
  • Enclosing class:
    OWLEnquirer

    public class OWLEnquirer.ClassRestriction
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a container for quantify class restrictions. It is produced fom OWLEnquirer.getClassRestrictions(OWLClass) and describes OWLClassExpression of the given class, if its type is one of: ClassExpressionType.OBJECT_SOME_VALUES_FROM, ClassExpressionType.DATA_SOME_VALUES_FROM (∃), ClassExpressionType.OBJECT_ALL_VALUES_FROM, ClassExpressionType.DATA_ALL_VALUES_FROM (∀), ClassExpressionType.OBJECT_MIN_CARDINALITY, ClassExpressionType.DATA_MIN_CARDINALITY, ClassExpressionType.OBJECT_MAX_CARDINALITY, ClassExpressionType.DATA_MAX_CARDINALITY, ClassExpressionType.OBJECT_EXACT_CARDINALITY, ClassExpressionType.DATA_EXACT_CARDINALITY. Where the getters of this containers depends from one of those types, assigned through setters.
